3FF43762.Line5.137EC4: But...it deserves to collect more than dust. To taste demon blood again. It should be in the hands of the worthy. One to wield it with purpose.

67708DA0.Line3.137EC4: Though the axe will take a new form, it will be stronger than ever.

8EECE3DE.Line1.137EC4: A sturdy horn and a fair amount of Silver Quartz. The ancestors led you well.

F0FB8AE6.Line9.137EC4: If you meet the Triune again, remind them of our strength. Oxen does not yield.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “I have what you need to repair the great axe.”
